title: J Cole & Dreamville - Revenge Of The Dreamers  mixtape
description:
J Cole and his Dreamville team surprise us with this new compilation project titled "Revenge Of The Dreamers". Celebrating J Cole's 29th birthday today with a major announcement. The Roc Nation MC has revealed that his Dreamville imprint has signed a partnership with Interscope Records, which ultimately led to the release of this new compilation project. The new 11-track mixtape features fellow Dreamville artists J. Cole, Bas, Omen, K-Quick, and Treasure Davis.


1.J Cole - Lil' Niggaz (Snippet) 
2.Bas - Golden Goals 
3.Omen - Motion Picture 
4.Bas - Lit (feat. J. Cole and K-Quick) 
5.J Cole - Revenge of the Dreamers 
6.Bas - Ceelo With the G's 
7.Omen - Henny Flow 
8.J Cole - Blowin Smoke 
9.J Cole - Bitchez (feat. Bas and Omen) 
10.Treasure Davis - May The Bitter Man Win (feat. J. Cole) 
11.J Cole - Crooked Smile (Original)
